blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Flaafitoed Flaafy and Politoed fusion Electric/Water type Ability: Fluffy The Jumping Puff Pokemon A very friendly pokefusion,...
caption:
Flaafitoed

Flaafy and Politoed fusion

Electric/Water type

Ability: Fluffy

The Jumping Puff Pokemon

A very friendly pokefusion, Flaffitoed moves by hopping.  It is known for being a great pokefusion to cuddle up to!  If you ever need cheering up, Flaffitoed is there!  It sometimes uses its water or electric abilities to boost its jump power.

Someone on our discord server requested this good bean!

summary:
A little spring comic for all you cacti growers out there. May your plants and Pokémon be healthy in the coming seasons!
Please...
body:
A little spring comic for all you cacti growers out there. May your plants and Pokémon be healthy in the coming seasons!

Please all be safe, use gloves, or some kind of protection while handing something so pointy. Some of the spines are barbed and don’t come out as easily as you’d like them to.

EDIT: I’ve gotten questions as to why sleep powder works on cacnea, it’s because it has very few spores in its system. It’s got no ability to learn or use sleep, poison or other powder based attacks and thus has no natrual remedy in its system for such things. Pokemon who know or can learn the attack are unaffected normally, but those who can’t learn it are just as susceptible as any normal Pokémon species would be. Least this is my head cannon haha

Please consider supporting me on my PATREON if you like the content, it helps a lot and let’s me make even more of it for all you lovely folk out there!
